e-switcher\">\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/\" hreflang=\"ja\"  data-current><abbr title=\"Japanese\">JP</abbr></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/company_en/\" hreflang=\"en\" ><abbr title=\"English\">EN</abbr></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/company_zhtw/\" hreflang=\"zh-TW\" ><abbr title=\"繁体中文\">繁中</abbr></a></li>\n</ul>            </div>\n          </div>\n        </nav>\n      </div>\n    </header>\n          <div class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-slide\">\n          <div class=\"hero-slide__item\">\n            <div class=\"hero__content\">\n              <p class=\"hero__en\"><span>Humans</span> <span>Take the Lead.</span></p>\n              <p class=\"hero__tagline\">人類が先。</p>\n              <p class=\"hero__text\">私たちは人のため、世界のために、<span class=\"break\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>進化するテクノロジーを使いこなし<span class=\"break\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>次の世代に誇れる未来を創造します。</p>\n            </div>\n            <img src=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/wp-content/themes/meistier/images/slides/01.webp\" srcset=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/wp-content/themes/meistier/images/slides/01.webp 1440w, https://www.meistier.co.jp/wp-content/themes/meistier/images/slides/01@2x.webp 2880w\" alt=\"\">\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"loader\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n      </div>\n        <div class=\"site-content site-content--home\">\n      <main id=\"main\">\n  <section class=\"home-news-area\">\n    <header class=\"home-news-area__header\">\n      <h2 class=\"home-section-heading\" data-en=\"News\">ニュース</h2>\n      <p>最新情報をお届けします</p>\n    </header>\n    <div class=\"home-news-area__content\">\n      <ul class=\"post-list\">\n        <li class=\"post-list__item\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/newscolumn/395/\" class=\"post-list__link\">\n    <time datetime=\"2026-06-10\" class=\"post-list__date\">2026.06.10</time>    <span class=\"post-list__category\">お知らせ</span>\n    <span class=\"post-list__title\">2026高校生と企業との交流会に出展</span>\n  </a>\n</li><li class=\"post-list__item\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/newscolumn/382/\" class=\"post-list__link\">\n    <time datetime=\"2026-05-27\" class=\"post-list__date\">2026.05.27</time>    <span class=\"post-list__category\">お知らせ</span>\n    <span class=\"post-list__title\">赤潮対策プロジェクトチーム成果報告会で「赤潮予測AI」について発表</span>\n  </a>\n</li><li class=\"post-list__item\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/newscolumn/374/\" class=\"post-list__link\">\n    <time datetime=\"2026-05-15\" class=\"post-list__date\">2026.05.15</time>    <span class=\"post-list__category\">お知らせ</span>\n    <span class=\"post-list__title\">AIでヒトの動作を解析し新たな医療バイタルサインとして活用する協業開発を発表</span>\n  </a>\n</li>      </ul>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"more-link\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/newscolumn/\" class=\"btn\">一覧をみる</a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"home-company-area\">\n    <div class=\"home-company-area__image\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><img src=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/wp-content/themes/meistier/images/home_company_img.webp\" srcset=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/wp-content/themes/meistier/images/home_company_img.webp 976w, https://www.meistier.co.jp/wp-content/themes/meistier/images/home_company_img@2x.webp 1952w\" sizes=\"(max-width:767px) 100vw, (max-width:1279px) 76.25vw, 976px\" width=\"976\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\"></div>\n    <div class=\"home-company-area__content\">\n      <h2 class=\"home-section-heading\" data-en=\"Company\">会社案内</h2>\n      <p class=\"tagline\">人と技術の力をつなぎ<wbr>社会を支える現場から<wbr>新しい未来を創る</p>\n      <div class=\"home-company-area__lede\">\n        <p>将来の予測が難しく不確実で変化が激しい時代。<br>\n          社会や産業の在り方が問われる今、<span class=\"break\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>私たちマイスティアは「人と技術の共進化」を掲げ、<span class=\"break\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>人財・AI・IoT・ロボティクスを融合した社会の実現に挑戦しています。<br>\n          環境変化に柔軟に対応しながら、現場から世界の未来を支える<br>\n          ――それが、私たちの使命です。</p>\n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"link-list\">\n        <li><a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/company/\">Vision</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/company/overview/\">概要・沿革</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/company/office/\">事業所</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/company/group/\">グループ企業・関連団体</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/company/iso/\">ISOへの取り組み</a></li>      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"home-business-area\">\n    <div class=\"home-business-area__content\">\n      <div class=\"home-business-area__bg\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <video src=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/wp-content/themes/meistier/images/bg_business.mp4\" playsinline autoplay muted loop></video>\n      </div>\n      <h2 class=\"home-section-heading\" data-en=\"Business\">事業案内</h2>\n      <p class=\"tagline\">地域の産業を技術で<wbr>サポートする</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"slide-wrap\">\n      <section class=\"business-slide splide\" aria-label=\"事業一覧\">\n        <div class=\"splide__track\">\n          <div class=\"splide__list\">\n            <section class=\"business-slide__item splide__slide\">\n              <div class=\"business-slide__image\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><img src=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/assets/images/business_image1_01.webp\" alt=\"\"></div>\n              <div class=\"business-slide__content\">\n                <h3 class=\"business-slide__title\" data-en=\"Embedded IoT System Development\">組込みIoTシステム開発</h3>\n                <p class=\"business-slide__tagline\">生産現場の「見える化」で<wbr>業務の効率化とデータ経営をサポート</p>\n              </div>\n              <a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/business/#iot\" class=\"btn\">詳細はこちら</a>\n            </section>\n            <section class=\"business-slide__item splide__slide\">\n              <div class=\"business-slide__image\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><img src=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/assets/images/business_image2_01.webp\" alt=\"\"></div>\n              <div class=\"business-slide__content\">\n                <h3 class=\"business-slide__title\" data-en=\"Smart Production System Development\">スマート生産システム開発</h3>\n                <p class=\"business-slide__tagline\">既存設備を活かしつつ<wbr>生産環境の最適化で労働力不足を解消</p>\n              </div>\n              <a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/business/#smartproduction\" class=\"btn\">詳細はこちら</a>\n            </section>\n            <section class=\"business-slide__item splide__slide\">\n              <div class=\"business-slide__image\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><img src=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/assets/images/business_image3_01.webp\" alt=\"\"></div>\n              <div class=\"business-slide__content\">\n                <h3 class=\"business-slide__title\" data-en=\"AI System Development\">AIシステム開発</h3>\n                <p class=\"business-slide__tagline\">機密性やプライバシーを配慮した<wbr>独自のAI開発</p>\n              </div>\n              <a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/business/#ai\" class=\"btn\">詳細はこちら</a>\n            </section>\n            <section class=\"business-slide__item splide__slide\">\n              <div class=\"business-slide__image\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><img src=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/assets/images/business_image4_01.webp\" alt=\"\"></div>\n              <div class=\"business-slide__content\">\n                <h3 class=\"business-slide__title\" data-en=\"Semiconductor Manufacturing Equipment Support\">半導体製造装置サポート</h3>\n                <p class=\"business-slide__tagline\">組立・検査・搬入まで<wbr>一貫したエンジニアリング支援体制</p>\n              </div>\n              <a href=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/business/#semiconductor\" class=\"btn\">詳細はこちら</a>\n            </section>\n            <section class=\"business-slide__item splide__slide\">\n              <div class=\"business-slide__image\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><img src=\"https://www.meistier.co.jp/assets/images/business_image5_01.webp\" alt=\"\"></div>\n              <div class=\"business-slide__content\">\n                <h3 class=\"business-slide__title\" data-en=\"Precision Machinery Main